description: [``botocore``] Support resolving regional API calls to partition's leader region endpoint.
[``botocore``] With this release, Bedrock Evaluation will now support latency-optimized inference for foundation models.
[``botocore``] Add support for DisconnectOnSessionTimeout flag in CreateClientVpnEndpoint and ModifyClientVpnEndpoint requests and DescribeClientVpnEndpoints responses
[``botocore``] Support updating connector configuration via UpdateConnector API. Release Operations API to monitor the status of the connector operation.
[``botocore``] This update provides tagging support for Transcribe's Call Analytics Jobs and Call Analytics Categories.
